            </div>
    <div class="c-billboard__sidebar">
      <div class="c-billboard__content">
        <div class="c-billboard__eyebrow">Petition</div>
        <h2 class="c-billboard__title">Urge the Biden administration to enact a strong Global Plastics Treaty</h2>
        <p>Plastic pollution has been linked to everything from cancer in humans to death in wildlife. A strong Global Plastics Treaty could help rid the world of harmful plastics—and as one of the world’s largest producers and consumers of plastic, the United States has a critical role to play.</p>

                  <div class="c-billboard__action">
            


<a  class="c-button" href="https://action.nrdc.org/letter/2965-global-plastics-treaty-041524?initms=WBSNAGPTPETC30424&amp;ms=WBSNAGPTPETC30424">    Take Action
  </a>          </div>
              </div>
    </div>
