  <div class="c-billboard__layout">
    <div class="c-billboard__media">                              
  
    <img loading="lazy" srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/medium_vertical_50/public/2024-04/RTXYVR6_RM-2926.jpg.webp?h=0f4230fa&amp;itok=-hnVkh2d 384w, /sites/default/files/styles/medium_vertical_100/public/2024-04/RTXYVR6_RM-2926.jpg.webp?h=0f4230fa&amp;itok=Y8hygq-j 768w, /sites/default/files/styles/medium_vertical_200/public/2024-04/RTXYVR6_RM-2926.jpg.webp?h=0f4230fa&amp;itok=F1Cm49o8 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 2.22222rem), 768px" width="384" height="576" src="/sites/default/files/styles/medium_vertical_100/public/2024-04/RTXYVR6_RM-2926.jpg.jpg?h=0f4230fa&amp;itok=Y8hygq-j" alt="Dead honeybees on a hive" />






            </div>
    <div class="c-billboard__sidebar">
      <div class="c-billboard__content">
        <div class="c-billboard__eyebrow">Petition</div>
        <h2 class="c-billboard__title">Tell the EPA to ban toxic neonics and save our food supply</h2>
        <p>Bees and other pollinators are dying at an alarming rate from toxic pesticides called neonics. Fewer bees means less food, and that could lead to increasing food costs, reduced access to healthier foods, and food scarcity.</p>

